**/runs/**/*.pth
TAbort-

# Orion smoke/test logs
.orion-smoke-logs/

# === GitNexus derived code-graph index (generated state, never authority) ===
.gitnexus/

# graphify's ephemeral pipeline state (interpreter path, scan root, detect
# cache, per-chunk extraction fragments, semantic-cache staging files, etc).
# Local scratch state written during a /graphify run, never meant to be
# tracked -- only graphify-out/graph.json, GRAPH_REPORT.md, and manifest.json
# are the real committed outputs. Left untracked repeatedly by past sessions
# (e.g. graphify-out/.graphify_python) and had to be cleaned up by hand.
graphify-out/.graphify_*

# graphify's local per-file extraction cache -- derived, reconstructable from
# graphify-out/graph.json via scripts/graphify_seed_semantic_cache.py. Never
# commit local cache files (CLAUDE.md section 2).
graphify-out/cache/
